WEBVTT

00:00.925 --> 00:04.625
As the CDC continues to study the spread of Covid-19,...

00:05.187 --> 00:10.395
...they're recommending that people wear cloth face coverings in public settings...

00:10.811 --> 00:14.551
...where social distancing measures can be difficult to maintain...

00:15.147 --> 00:18.172
...such as grocery stores and pharmacies.

00:18.907 --> 00:23.973
Remember, this does not replace the importance of social distancing.

00:24.843 --> 00:29.753
It's another recommended guideline  to keep us all safe.

